Sometimes it is more efficient to run [[Puppet]] via [[cron]] instead of a daemon:
<pre>
  cron { "puppet":
      command => "/usr/bin/puppet agent -t --logdest syslog > /dev/null 2>&1",
      user => "root",
      minute => fqdn_rand( 60 ),
      ensure => present,
  }
</pre>

